```{r, message=FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
library(palmerpenguins)
```


Here is a scatterplot of two variables from the `penguins` dataset: flipper length in millimeters and body mass in grams. The points are colored based on the penguin species.

```{r}

ggplot(penguins, aes(x = flipper_length_mm, y = body_mass_g, color = species)) +
  geom_point()

